daring divine delbert a fan of mr. d 's for many years and appreciating his uniqueness and sense of humor always shown in his music . track # 8 down in mexico is a song not to be missed with anyone with ears muchless a fan . saw delbert perform it live on 2/14/06 in lex ky the best sound i 've ever heard in concert ; any genre . this cd offers subtle surprises and big smiles . pashaswife